title: Justice League: The New Frontier [2008]DVDRip[Eng]Xvid-[2C]
description:
I finally got my hands on the real DVD of this movie. No offence to PiPE (or anyone else), but I prefer my movies at 2 CD size, not one. I have added a sample video since that seems to help make things go easier for many people.

This continues to be ripped like everything else I do, so expect no surprises. I included the history of the Justice League extra as part of this. It is no light weight at over 40 minutes long itself. I also kept the two English commentary tracks in the main movie.

Enjoy.
